Comment: 0,0:01:42.35,0:01:43.14,SC_Bottom,甘奈,0,200,0,kara,嗯\Nうん
Comment: 0,0:01:42.35,0:01:43.14,SC_Bottom,甜花,200,0,0,kara,嗯\Nうん
